DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T193000Z
UID:9f44155892778aa6539e59b16e868dcf@northwestern.edu
DESCRIPTION:The Evanston Dance Ensemble is diving into the archives. Join 
 us as we explore the culture\, attitude\, and expansive reach of rock and 
 roll music. Artistic Director Enid Smith and Assistant to the Director Mac
 ala Bartucci are joined by guests Kaleigh Dent\, Julie Cartier\, Tori Isaa
 c\, Ro Goodman\, and EDE founding director Béa Rashid in this electrifyin
 g evening of dance.\nSuggested ages: Suitable for children\nApproximate Ru
 n Time: TBD\nLate seating is allowed during applause
LOCATION:Wirtz Center: Josephine Louis Theater\, 20 Arts Circle Drive\, Ev
 anston\, IL
URL:https://ci.ovationtix.com/1771/production/1263820
X-SOURCE:Northwestern University
END:VEVENT
