DTSTART;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260425T003000Z
DTEND;TZID=UTC;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260425T020000Z
UID:9c401daab7067d4cbb348ba09fad81e4@northwestern.edu
DESCRIPTION:Donald Schleicher\, conductor\; Shihan Jin\, graduate assistan
 t conductor\nLili Boulanger\, D’un matin de printemps (Of a Spring Morni
 ng)\nRichard Strauss\, Don Juan\, Op. 20\nIgor Stravinsky\, Le sacre du pr
 intemps (The Rite of Spring)
