UID:c2e8be10f7c22e921504f616fa252783@northwestern.edu
DESCRIPTION:Derrick Gardner\, conductor\; Ari Hoenig\, drums\nThe Jazz Orc
 hestra welcomes guest drummer Ari Hoenig for their first concert of the sp
 ring quarter. Dubbed a “postbop daredevil” (Time Out New York) for who
 m “rhythm is a contact sport” (New York Times)\, Hoenig has performed 
 with the Kenny Werner Trio\, the Chris Potter Underground\, and the Joshua
  Redman Elastic Band\, as well as bands led by Wayne Krantz\, Mike Stern\,
  Richard Bona\, and Pat Martino. He has led the Ari Hoenig Quartet since 2
 002 and is a faculty member at New York University and the New School for 
 Social Research.
